urdu transliteration text:
Wo Zulm Deikhey Hain Sajjad Ne Hussain Ke Baad,Mujhe Yaqeen Hai Ke Ab Tak Bhi Ro Raha Hoga
What pain and suffering did Sajjad face after Hussain’s [death],
@HujjatELC

Jo Ghaur Keejey To Abid Bashar Nahi Lagta,Mere Khyaal Mein Dukh Dard Ka Khuda Hoga
Upon reflection his patience seems to be beyond capacity,
@HujjatELC
